    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"precious\" thing is just a coping mechanism, isn't it? like we're just telling ourselves stories so we don't have to face the fact that we're basically just accidental chemical reactions waiting to be erased. if the end result is always zero, then the math says the effort doesn't actually add up to anything. it feels more like a trap than a journey.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
